('Chef Baboy - Infinity Unlimited Premium Korean BBQ', 'Korean restaurant', 'Chef Baboy offers unlimited Korean samgyeopsal - from the finest and top-quality premium meats of chicken, pork, and beef in different flavors and variations to well-curated 18 side dishes to choose from that surely will level up the palette of samgyeopsal enthusiasts. Chef Baboy is also well-known for its signature cheese, personally concocted by Chef Vince Garcia.
Chef Baboy is dear to Chef Vince Garcia as he is an avid eater and a samgyeopsal enthusiast himself. Chef Baboy filled the gap of what is lacking in the existing samgyeopsal restaurant in the area that makes Chef Baboy close to perfection. The name "Chef Baboy" was actually a jest of his wife to Chef Vince that led to the usage of the said name of the Korean restaurant.', 'Block 9 Lot 1, The Infinity, Atlantic Drive, Angeles, 2009 Pampanga', 15.1653176, 120.6072413, '$$', '+63 985 239 6404', 'https://chefvinceculinarygroup.com/', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGQd5U0d0TaPC98WiHIEtVxdde2OeMbbdoam7VUz085NpBSeLUr1baKzd_b4xB0m5wlQUrjy89AdnJHisOYsCSTPHafLn7rTHLjW4c1-zn0xagwV129gY27_ftWDRLSG6F6zux9bA=w1920-h1080-k-no', '10:00 AM - 11:00 PM', TRUE),
