('The Vintage Hall - 24 hour Brunch Club', 'Restaurant', '24-Hour Brunch Club!

The Vintage Hall is a 24-hour restaurant in Angeles City near Clark Freeport Zone, serving trendy and artisanal cuisine for both breakfast/brunch and dinner. Specializing in wood-fire baked dishes, Angus steaks, international-grade Filipino cuisine, and a comprehensive emphasis on healthy, organic and farm-to-table fare from smoothie bowls to vegan dishes.', 'ABC Hotel, 21st Street, Don Juico Ave, Angeles, 2009 Pampanga', 15.1660278, 120.581626, '$', '+63 917 701 5880', 'https://vintagehall.ph/', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFFC82G34GSPWpz7LPf36dxRSc0bYyvOcbHVP7LqOuJud42CSCOfgG7NZQ1rPPzMB7VID1T8phOeayHzJShuG1WjsHqm8o4igSxDd40nyZmNYBQELyTIZyzky2Kf6KuyZtsrvcDaA=w1920-h1080-k-no', '12:00 AM - 12:00 AM', TRUE),
('Scots Restaurant & Cafe', 'Restaurant', 'Welcome to Scots Restaurant & Cafe, your ultimate spot for fantastic food, great times, and delightful treats. Conveniently located on Zeppelin Street in Angeles City, we serve a diverse menu that blends American classics with global flavors. Indulge in our awesome burgers, tender steaks, flavor-packed pizzas, tasty pasta, fresh salads, loaded subs, mouthwatering chicken wings, big breakfasts, and traditional Filipino food. Plus, explore our large selection of premium coffee, refreshing drinks, and delectable desserts. Our lively atmosphere is perfect for hanging out with family and friends, whether for breakfast, casual dinners, or special celebrations. Friendly service and a welcoming environment await you at Scots Restaurant & Cafe.', '26 Zeppelin, Malabanas, Angeles, 2009 Pampanga', 15.1593844, 120.5813123, '$$', '+63 969 571 8999', 'http://www.scots.ph/', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHD6rM4mHeDM-PFSUZLccJp9qFNBBoemuKMUdVHMiTWs__L1j8-EUA3d-lVZkVeO8B1B7NOJJDliMKjGHbB4tgKKdNPySBuxUHU7r9q4lBY_0aUsopXzdsvP1GCNkJ60ooE9nYE=w1920-h1080-k-no', '07:00 AM - 11:00 PM', TRUE),
