('Smokey Yard Restaurant', 'Restaurant', 'Discover Smokey Yard, Angeles City''s premier destination for authentic and fresh Halal cuisine. Specializing in flavorful, family-style grilled chicken, tender beef, and fresh seafood, our menu also features savory noodles and generous rice meals. Conveniently located in the heart of Angeles, we are the perfect choice for both locals and travelers seeking a memorable dining experience. Our welcoming, family-friendly atmosphere offers a relaxed dine-in setting, complete with shisha and refreshing drinks. For your next event, we also provide Halal party trays for easy takeout. Come and taste the best Halal grilled specialties Pampanga has to offer.', 'Nepo Mart Complex, Catalina St, Angeles, 2009 Pampanga', 15.1360559, 120.5862909, '$', '+63 905 774 2428', NULL, 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGbPVJiKGXdViu2LNdF0z98ndMLpzUDTkA9G7mK5ISg-D-wZWw5jajaMPVh-sqKMi1PU73DVCqVK0G83-NNC8JM5pmHrNa7y1C7fSnQ9mI4aAfvLZ2TWz3wH9WoeTvdCJN0f4IM0QVyiYtX=w1920-h1080-k-no', '10:00 AM - 10:00 PM', TRUE),
